-> ssm/design/source-diagnostics
-> ssm/design/source-hit-provenance
-> ssm/design/source-origin-locator
-> ssm/design/source-publication-boundary
-> ssm/design/source-registry
> Stage a fully source-bound initial publication; do not publish an aggregate compatibility bridge.
> Retained legacy artifacts are migration input only, never reader-visible source state.
> The first fully source-bound publication activates the control-plane reader and replaces legacy public reader behavior without overlap.
